>Sometimes rich assholes get what they deserve.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/ufHAXF3</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/MDH4vSH.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>He actually treated me pretty well. Paid me decent and even gave me flexible hours when I was going through chemo.

He was always sketchy with everyone else though. I have a bunch of stories but basically, I always described him like Trump. He lied constantly, refused to pay people, and always had some kind of scam going. 

The FBI couldn't tell me any details about their investigation but I'm pretty sure it has to do with financial crimes like tax fraud and insurance fraud.

MOST VITAL EDIT:

Thanks! I'm not gonna ask for anything, just try to address the most interesting, relevant questions.

1.  I definitely thought about getting a lawyer and I agree it's sound advice. I had nothing to hide and I believe they had no interest in implicating me. I'm confident they were genuinely asking for a favor and, tbh, I couldn't afford a lawyer anyway. Also, it was a very short interview. 30 minutes. 

2. The interviewers never asked me to keep our conversation a secret so I'm not concerned about impeding an ongoing investigation. One of the first questions they asked me was if anyone had already contacted me about the investigation (they hadn't).

3. This was a restaurant that I helped open but I haven't worked there in over 3 years and the owner closed it down, retired, and moved to the other side of the country pre-covid.

4. He did treat me well but I watched him screw over a lot of people. He got banned from Costco for stealing, I'm pretty sure he committed insurance fraud while I was employed.  He was an arrogant bully and a clearly had no shame or integrity.

5. Finally, to the "snitch" comment and the other related ones. Knowing imgur, I feel confident that those were just sarcastic jokes that didn't land well. Just in case though, this wasn't a single mother stealing a loaf of bread. This was a millionaire with sociopathic tenancies that hurt so many people that now the FBI is involved. Even if I had loyalties to him (I don't) I value my own integrity over covering up a crime for such a selfish criminal.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/ufHAXF3</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[meme2theextreme]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>No difference</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/tal2Md4</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/6La2wI9.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/tal2Md4</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[Srajo101]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Crying happy tears</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/lvpU1QE</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Goof8yJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Mi amorcito had a hysterectomy today. Finally found a doctor that not only was willing but encouraged the surgery. Good thing she did because it was worse than we thought.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/sDpD84y.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>After years of first hand witnessing my partner suffer, she’s finally on the up on feeling better</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/7LsV0RG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Hxr2BYw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Our pizza Pablo for the dog tax</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/lvpU1QE</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[ClassicShay]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Spot on.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/xMZQYSA</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/df6648N.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>But some random verse about “knowing you in the womb” is justification for taking people’s rights away.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/xMZQYSA</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[actinginacave]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Keep Fighting.</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/arfMpYe</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/GF9JrrG.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>As a white cis male, I'll never know what it's like to feel like I can't get something I want in my life and that's lost on so many other men and women in this country. I feel it in my soul it's not my RIGHT to tell anyone what to do with their life and it's certainly not anyone's business how or if a woman chooses to keep or terminate a pregnancy. That decision lies with that woman her healthcare team and who she chooses to involve in that decision. If you don't get that simple idea, you are part of the problem and do not see how this starts a ball rolling we'll never be able to stop.

Edit: love all of the conversations happening. If your took time to read through this, take time to get involved in your community, if not for you, for the person who needs you. Be Safe.</div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/49HqUmI.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>Dag tax.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/arfMpYe</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[HeirElfSquire]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Fascist Fake Christian MAGA</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/yzDgbSi</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Cd0rzm2.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/yzDgbSi</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[WalkGood]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>THT Amazons... :)</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/DVc5eS0</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/IAKFPb8.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/dS3ZcIK.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/5uGh3By.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/1VYNMMF.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/wt6PHEw.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/xEW53Id.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/RB9wYBO.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/gGKjiNq.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/T0MJWyu.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><di